.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUipIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=ffd6293f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/requesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens</a><br />\n<br />\n大家繼續幫手文宣 各自爬山 山頂見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085cbad4e6c0882b9643c21b2210baffc7889d9f","tid":1353411,"uid":48011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23e29192c8e55cb0eac0c70e43e4458098411869","tid":1353411,"uid":114580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:12:34.000Z","msg":"對家諗緊乜 先會肯同呢隻冇腦豬做隊友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:14:35.000Z","msg":"佢地都冇腦點會諗到野"},{"pid":"86363f8216a23a4a2170ae691360499a63f0a68e","tid":1353411,"uid":208875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:14:38.000Z","msg":"用力推"},{"pid":"91f4c58e487b5cbea0a73b494e6b098db3502518","tid":1353411,"uid":264136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a182316884ae05a0ba67e7d8cf85a71476937956","tid":1353411,"uid":69215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:43:14.000Z","msg":"屌你班仆街727點部署又唔撚講係推d垃圾post,南邊圍剪光纖呢d垃圾post都推到上熱門。集中返講727先。<br />\n<br />\n下面係我既建議：<br />\n我地要定性元朗727事件係「反黑警勾結運動」要放到呢樣野最大，號招所有和理派出黎。<br />\n<br />\n勇武就保護所有和平集會/遊行人士，人夠多就會有警察所以相對班黑唔夠膽搞我地 如果夠膽搞班勇武就可以出手自衛打到佢地仆街，最好帶埋索帶制服。<br />\n<br />\n勇武派當日亦大條道理武裝，因為我地認為警黑勾結，人民需要自組自衞隊。和理非亦大條道理cover勇武，因為班黑警見到你班勇武一定直接拉何況我地咁楊<br />\n<br />\n1. 目標「反黑警勾結」運動要求政府馬上調查元朗警方同黑社會勾結。<br />\n<br />\n2. 唔建議燒村，因為其實而家所謂圍村好多係外性人，好多自己友。<br />\n<br />\n3. 要佔可以佔元朗大馬路，因為元朗警署對住大馬路位置，夠位置比和理非佔領。<br />\n<br />\n4.如果班黑社會夠膽出刀手即管黎，我係和班非預左食一兩刀，但事件夠新閒帶風向話比全香港人知元朗黑社會問題有機嚴重，何況我地有勇武保護<br />\n<br />\n5. 我地定性係和平集會，報界朋友可以幫手宣傳<br />\n<br />\n6. 屯元天朋友馬上用telegram 自組自衛隊，走個下cover所有人走<br />\n<br />\n最後想講兄弟各自爬山不分化，和理非都要同我出撚曬黎cover勇武派唔好比佢地比人拉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1353394\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1353394</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3466ca417a67515447b756d5c74a7511671b3678","tid":1353411,"uid":264136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00492cc95853ad9cf57e743145e4ea0b7ad35e4b","tid":1353411,"uid":158417,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:03:24.000Z","msg":"係咪要幫何妖back up定佢facebook d片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論是前往美國公幹、留學或旅行，都先要到美國領事館申請簽證，美國政府去年計劃對簽證申請者加強背景審查，日前美國國務院終於推出新規定。所有申請者都需要將其社交平台帳號名稱，連同電話號碼和過去 5 年用過的電郵地址一併提交，預計每年將會有大約 1,500 萬申請簽證人士受到影響，當中 1,400 萬人屬非移民簽證的申請者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/unwire.hk/2019/06/03/us-visa-now-requires-applicants-social-media-info/life-tech/travel/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F03%2Fus-visa-now-requires-applicants-social-media-info%2Flife-tech%2Ftravel%2Famp%2F&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUipIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=352c00c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/unwire.hk/2019/06/03/us-visa-now-requires-applicants-social-media-info/life-tech/travel/amp/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ed2a3151f844b2bb3ab4e3aaf0494e45634b91","tid":1353411,"uid":264136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ee944f98f7e4d7bad957ada1547f1bd064f4ab6a","tid":1353411,"uid":286832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:08:54.000Z","msg":"<spa